Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:04.15,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}我想了解一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:08.24,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}说给我听
